    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a genus containing 38 living species of small rodents that usually have a pointed snout, relatively large eyes and ears, and a long tail, and typically feed on seeds and fruit.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
